---
/**
 * Theme Extensions Gallery
 *
 * Overview of all experimental theme extensions.
 */

import LabLayout from '../../../layouts/LabLayout.astro';
---

<LabLayout
  title="Theme Extensions"
  description="Experimental theme extensions for Vanilla Breeze: motion tokens, backgrounds, fonts, and more."
>
  <layout-center>
    <layout-stack>
      <header>
        <h1>Theme Extensions</h1>
        <p class="intro">
          Exploring new capabilities for the Vanilla Breeze theme system: motion,
          backgrounds, fonts, borders, and more.
        </p>
      </header>

      <nav class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/lab/">Lab</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span>Theme Extensions</span>
      </nav>

      <div class="demo-grid">
        <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/motion-tokens/" class="demo-card">
          <span class="demo-number">01</span>
          <h2>Motion Tokens</h2>
          <p>Expanded motion system with hover effects, transition presets, staggered animations, and View Transitions API integration.</p>
          <div class="demo-tags">
            <span class="demo-tag">Hover Effects</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Stagger</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">View Transitions</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/backgrounds/" class="demo-card">
          <span class="demo-number">02</span>
          <h2>Backgrounds & Surfaces</h2>
          <p>Page and component backgrounds beyond solid colors: gradients, noise textures, glassmorphism, and animated backgrounds.</p>
          <div class="demo-tags">
            <span class="demo-tag">Gradients</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Textures</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Glassmorphism</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/rough-borders/" class="demo-card">
          <span class="demo-number">03</span>
          <h2>Rough Borders</h2>
          <p>Non-standard border treatments using SVG filters, border-image, mask-image, and CSS techniques for sketchy themes.</p>
          <div class="demo-tags">
            <span class="demo-tag">SVG Filters</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Border Image</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Mask</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/custom-fonts/" class="demo-card">
          <span class="demo-number">04</span>
          <h2>Custom Fonts</h2>
          <p>External font loading with Google Fonts, variable fonts, display/body pairings, and font loading API patterns.</p>
          <div class="demo-tags">
            <span class="demo-tag">Google Fonts</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Variable Fonts</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Font Loading</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/lab/theme-extensions/sound-effects/" class="demo-card">
          <span class="demo-number">05</span>
          <h2>Sound Effects</h2>
          <p>Experimental audio feedback using Web Audio API. Click, hover, success, and error sounds with user preference controls.</p>
          <div class="demo-tags">
            <span class="demo-tag">Web Audio API</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">Experimental</span>
            <span class="demo-tag">User Prefs</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </layout-stack>
  </layout-center>
</LabLayout>

<style>
  header {
    margin-block-end: var(--size-m);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: var(--size-2xl);
    margin-block-end: var(--size-s);
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: var(--size-m);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--size-xs);
    font-size: var(--size-s);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-block-end: var(--size-l);
  }

  .breadcrumb a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .demo-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--size-m);
  }

  .demo-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: var(--size-l);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-m);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  }

  .demo-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .demo-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-block-end: var(--size-s);
  }

  .demo-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--size-xs) 0;
    font-size: var(--size-l);
  }

  .demo-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--size-s);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .demo-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--size-xs);
    margin-block-start: var(--size-m);
  }

  .demo-tag {
    padding: 0.125rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-surface-alt);
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
</style>
